<span class="line"><span style="color:#A6E3A1;">                &quot;Command blocked: &#39;</span><span style="color:#9399B2;">{}</span><span style="color:#A6E3A1;">&#39;. Reason: potential data exfiltration.&quot;</span><span style="color:#9399B2;">,</span></span>
